44
00:03:37,535 --> 00:03:40,434
dia jadi bingung

45
00:03:40,435 --> 00:03:42,334
jadi mungkin dia tidak ingat

46
00:03:42,335 --> 00:03:44,534
panjang sebenar parut itu.

47
00:03:44,535 --> 00:03:46,534
Lagipun, saya rasa pembunuh itu

48
00:03:46,535 --> 00:03:49,435
