60
00:04:24,035 --> 00:04:27,234
Lagipun, reaksi luminol yang selalunya boleh mengesan

61
00:04:27,235 --> 00:04:29,534
kesan darah walaupun selepas dilap

62
00:04:29,535 --> 00:04:32,634
