63
00:04:32,635 --> 00:04:35,034
Parut ketiga-tiga lelaki itu.

64
00:04:35,035 --> 00:04:38,134
Ada satu parut besar di bahagian belakang Encik Kusumoto

65
00:04:38,135 --> 00:04:40,834
