66
00:04:40,835 --> 00:04:43,735
Di bahagian belakang Encik Hoya ada parut kecil.

67
00:04:44,735 --> 00:04:47,534
Encik Kusumoto kurus semasa dia masih kecil

68
00:04:47,535 --> 00:04:50,534
