Sudah tentulah susyi premium.

104
00:06:40,735 --> 00:06:42,634
Apa kata kamu pun makan, pelayan?

105
00:06:42,635 --> 00:06:46,034
Kurumi suruh kamu makan bersama-sama kami.

106
00:06:46,035 --> 00:06:47,534
Ya.

107
00:06:47,535 --> 00:06:48,835
Baiklah.

108
00:06:55,735 --> 00:06:59,434
Bahan semula jadi memang bagus.

109
