167
00:09:40,435 --> 00:09:44,034
Badan saya bersaiz besar semasa saya kecil.

168
00:09:44,035 --> 00:09:45,334
Saya pun.

169
00:09:45,335 --> 00:09:47,234
Encik Kusumoto.

170
00:09:47,235 --> 00:09:51,834
