171
00:09:51,835 --> 00:09:54,234
Ya...

172
00:09:54,235 --> 00:09:57,034
Mungkin dia kata dia kurus

173
00:09:57,035 --> 00:09:58,634
selepas mendengar yang budak lelaki yang dicarinya

174
00:09:58,635 --> 00:10:00,734
diberi nama timang-timangan Gari.

175
00:10:00,735 --> 00:10:03,134
Mungkin dia fikir ia "gari-gari" yang bermaksud kurus.

176
00:10:03,135 --> 00:10:05,234
Dia diberi nama timang-timangan Gari

